title: Ezekiel Elliott, Baker Mayfield, NFL hope, and WR duos
itunes:title: Ezekiel Elliott, Baker Mayfield, NFL hope, and WR duos
description:
Colin talks about how immature players like Ezekiel Elliott can hurt teams, Baker Mayfield's recent comments on Hue Jackson, teams who have a chance to win it all, and his thoughts on the best WR duos in the NFL. Guests include Danny Kanell, Kevin O'Connor, Matt Mosley, and Shawne Merriman.
